product_name: ASICS Gel-Instinct33 Running Shoes - Men's - 2012 Closeout
long_description: Ideal for everyday runs on gravel roads or dirt paths, the ASICS GEL-Instinct 33 Running Shoes for men are built on a well-cushioned platform with trail-specific tread for great traction. Cushioned and flexible, ASICS GEL-Instinct 33 running shoes have a lightweight, natural feel. Seamless polyurethane overlay and mesh-fused uppers add stability and keep out grit. Solyte(R) midsole is lighter in weight than standard EVA; GEL(R) heel cushioning provides comfort on long training runs. Propulsion Trusstic(R) in forefoot helps your foot launch you forward more quickly. Vertical flex groove down center of sole enhances gait efficiency. Multidirectional lugs on the soles provide traction when you're going up and down steep trails. Closeout.
